ITC Rises After Report Cigarette Prices Raised on Tax Increase

-- B y   S u b r a m a n i a m   S h a r m a
-- 
2011-09-23T03:49:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/itc-rises-after-report-cigarette-prices-raised-on-tax-increase.html
ITC Ltd. (ITC)  gained as much as 1.8
percent in Mumbai trading after the Business Standard newspaper
reported the company has increased prices of its mid-sized
cigarette brand, following an increase in value-added tax on
cigarettes in southern Andhra Pradesh state to 20 percent from
14.5 percent.   The stock rose 1.4 percent to 193.55 rupees as of 9:18 a.m.
local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Subramaniam Sharma at 
 ssharma@bloomberg.net  